name: Target Practice (itch) (vladventura)
description:
This project was made for Software Engineering 1 homework, Design 1, by Vladimir Ventura.

I made this itch.io page to make it easier for whoever has to grade this homework; instead of downloading my whole project they can instead play it online, and there's also the option to download the Windows version as well.

Due to my time constraint, I consider this project done. There are some things that I wish I had the time to fix, alas I can't.

I may come back to this project later on in life and extend it until I am truly happy with it.

Please don't donate, I really won't take money for doing homework.
